aa(lp12
VIt was my first week in federal prison,
p13
aVand I was learning quickly that it wasn't what you see on TV.
p14
aVIn fact, it was teeming with smart, ambitious men
p15
aVwhose business instincts were in many cases
p16
aVas sharp as those of the CEOs
p17
aVwho had wined and dined me six months earlier
p18
